ynote session, we will explore how digital is transforming businesses and organisations, and chart a path for a new approach to developing, deploying, and managing digital services that are fast, seamless, and optimized from mainframe to mobile to cloud and beyond.'),(2650,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_1_session_info','field_56afdd1a0e967'),(2651,2038,'session_cards_sep6_2_title','Coffee in Solutions Area'),(2652,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_2_title','field_56afdcfb0e964'),(2653,2038,'session_cards_sep6_2_time','10.30 – 11.00am'),(2654,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_2_time','field_56afdd070e965'),(2655,2038,'session_cards_sep6_2_font_awesome_icon','fa-coffee'),(2656,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_2_font_awesome_icon','field_56afdd100e966'),(2657,2038,'session_cards_sep6_2_session_info',''),(2658,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_2_session_info','field_56afdd1a0e967'),(2659,2038,'session_cards_sep6_3_title','The Evolution of IT to Digital Service Management'),(2660,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_3_title','field_56afdcfb0e964'),(2661,2038,'session_cards_sep6_3_time','11.00 – 11.45am'),(2662,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_3_time','field_56afdd070e965'),(2663,2038,'session_cards_sep6_3_font_awesome_icon','fa-wrench'),(2664,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_3_font_awesome_icon','field_56afdd100e966'),(2665,2038,'session_cards_sep6_3_session_info',''),(2666,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_3_session_info','field_56afdd1a0e967'),(2667,2038,'session_cards_sep6_4_title','BMC Smart IT, BMC MyIT, and the Power of the Next-Generation Service Platform'),(2668,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_4_title','field_56afdcfb0e964'),(2669,2038,'session_cards_sep6_4_time','11.45 – 12.30pm'),(2670,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_4_time','field_56afdd070e965'),(2671,2038,'session_cards_sep6_4_font_awesome_icon','fa-stack-overflow'),(2672,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_4_font_awesome_icon','field_56afdd100e966'),(2673,2038,'session_cards_sep6_4_session_info','<div class=\"symple-column symple-four-fifth symple-column-last\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<b>Alex Henson</b>, Principal Solution Marketing Manager, Service Management, BMC\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"symple-column symple-four-fifth symple-column-last\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nA key secret behind transformative services, such as Uber and Lyft, has been the service platform their applications provide—directly linking the consumer to the service provider in a new, dynamic way. In this session, we will show you how the latest developments in Smart IT and MyIT have brought this exciting vision of integrated service to ITSM. Smart IT’s optimised UX and assistive behavior enables calls to be logged 20% faster and with 35% better resolution rates. MyIT can help reduce up to 90% of your calls in the first place. Mobility for everyone, inside and outside the office, gets things done faster.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),(2674,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_4_session_info','field_56afdd1a0e967'),(2675,2038,'session_cards_sep6_5_title','Lunch – Solutions Area'),(2676,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_5_title','field_56afdcfb0e964'),(2677,2038,'session_cards_sep6_5_time','12.30 – 1.00pm'),(2678,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_5_time','field_56afdd070e965'),(2679,2038,'session_cards_sep6_5_font_awesome_icon','fa-spoon'),(2680,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_5_font_awesome_icon','field_56afdd100e966'),(2681,2038,'session_cards_sep6_5_session_info',''),(2682,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_5_session_info','field_56afdd1a0e967'),(2683,2038,'session_cards_sep6_6_title','Data Center Discovery for the Digital Era'),(2684,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_6_title','field_56afdcfb0e964'),(2685,2038,'session_cards_sep6_6_time','1.00 – 2.45pm'),(2686,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_6_time','field_56afdd070e965'),(2687,2038,'session_cards_sep6_6_font_awesome_icon','fa-cc-discover'),(2688,2038,'_session_cards_sep6_6_font_awesome_icon','field_56afdd100e966'),(2689,2038,'session_cards_sep6_6_session_info','Learn how data center discovery provides foundational data that supports Digital Service Management and get a preview of what is coming in