sion_paralela1_0_session_info','field_586e18d380844'),(5880,2068,'session_paralela2_0_title','Workload Automation in the Agile Enterprise'),(5881,2068,'_session_paralela2_0_title','field_586e18d399076'),(5882,2068,'session_paralela2_0_time','1:00 – 1:25'),(5883,2068,'_session_paralela2_0_time','field_586e18d3991c2'),(5884,2068,'session_paralela2_0_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5885,2068,'_session_paralela2_0_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d39930b'),(5886,2068,'session_paralela2_0_session_info','Accelerating delivery of new business services is driving organizations to radically modify their processes and their tools. What was once inconceivable; daily pushes to production, multi-disciplinary teams and scores of open- source technologies is today\'s new normal.<br/><br/>\r\nWithin this context, batch automation remains a fundamental management discipline that continues to be a critical component of almost every application. Being able to effectively manage batch in the new world of continuous integration/continuous delivery is mandatory for companies to automate delivery of new services on time and with greater operational quality than ever before. This session introduces the exciting new  capabilities BMC is adding to the Control-M platform that enable developers and DevOps teams to fully integrate batch and workflow management into their application delivery pipelines.'),(5887,2068,'_session_paralela2_0_session_info','field_586e18d399453'),(5888,2068,'session_paralela3_0_title','Digital Services at Digital Speed'),(5889,2068,'_session_paralela3_0_title','field_586e18d3b3b27'),(5890,2068,'session_paralela3_0_time','1:00 – 1:45'),(5891,2068,'_session_paralela3_0_time','field_586e18d3b3c8c'),(5892,2068,'session_paralela3_0_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5893,2068,'_session_paralela3_0_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3b3df1'),(5894,2068,'session_paralela3_0_session_info','Digital Transformation is a reality for almost every company. Implementing and adopting new technologies and processes have become mainstream but how do you adapt your existing infrastructure to provide what is needed in today’s digital environment? Learn how BMC TrueSight is working with you through this transformation. This session will introduce you to the TrueSight solution set, explain the overall vision and provide a solution level roadmap.'),(5895,2068,'_session_paralela3_0_session_info','field_586e18d3b3f4b'),(5896,2068,'session_paralela4_0_title','Innovate, Automate and Secure Your Digital Transformation'),(5897,2068,'_session_paralela4_0_title','field_586e18d3cf72b'),(5898,2068,'session_paralela4_0_time','1:00 – 1:45'),(5899,2068,'_session_paralela4_0_time','field_586e18d3cf876'),(5900,2068,'session_paralela4_0_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5901,2068,'_session_paralela4_0_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3cf9bf'),(5902,2068,'session_paralela4_0_session_info','In today’s world, consumer expectations are rising, change is accelerating and innovative software is disrupting industries. Transforming your business requires innovative applications and services that run on an increasingly automated and secure IT environment. Companies that embrace digital innovation more effectively than their competitors will be rewarded with higher profitability and increased valuations. In this session, you will learn how you can take actions now to improve your ability to innovate faster, to create industrialized automation and to simplify security and compliance.'),(5903,2068,'_session_paralela4_0_session_info','field_586e18d3cfb07'),(5906,2585,'_edit_lock','1484032411:6'),(5907,2585,'_edit_last','6'),(5908,2586,'_wp_attached_file','2017/01/Renato-Bonomini.jpg'),(5909,2586,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:160;s:6:\"height\";i:160;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2017/01/Renato-Bonomini.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Renato-Bonomini-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s