2068,'session_paralela1_4_session_info',''),(5957,2068,'_session_paralela1_4_session_info','field_586e18d380844'),(5958,2068,'session_paralela1_5_title','Developer Experience using Innovation Suite'),(5959,2068,'_session_paralela1_5_title','field_586e18d380467'),(5960,2068,'session_paralela1_5_time','4:00 – 4:45'),(5961,2068,'_session_paralela1_5_time','field_586e18d3805b3'),(5962,2068,'session_paralela1_5_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5963,2068,'_session_paralela1_5_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3806fc'),(5964,2068,'session_paralela1_5_session_info','Immerse yourself in the new developer experience at BMC! In this session, we’ll walk you through a developer’s role and engagement with the BMC Developer Ecosystem you will:\r\nLearn about the BMC Developer program and how you can get started\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get access to Developer sandbox and resources gain insight into the various developer programs and events happening in your neighborhood</li>\r\n	<li>Learn how to build and showcase your Personal brand by publishing &amp; sharing developer innovations</li>\r\n	<li>We’ll also show you a quick demo of “Building an App” using the Innovation Suite</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),(5965,2068,'_session_paralela1_5_session_info','field_586e18d380844'),(5966,2068,'session_paralela2_1_title','TBD:  Customer Case Study'),(5967,2068,'_session_paralela2_1_title','field_586e18d399076'),(5968,2068,'session_paralela2_1_time','1:25 – 1:45'),(5969,2068,'_session_paralela2_1_time','field_586e18d3991c2'),(5970,2068,'session_paralela2_1_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5971,2068,'_session_paralela2_1_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d39930b'),(5972,2068,'session_paralela2_1_session_info',''),(5973,2068,'_session_paralela2_1_session_info','field_586e18d399453'),(5974,2068,'session_paralela2_2_title','Introducing the All-New Control-M Managed File Transfer Solution'),(5975,2068,'_session_paralela2_2_title','field_586e18d399076'),(5976,2068,'session_paralela2_2_time','2:00 – 2:45'),(5977,2068,'_session_paralela2_2_time','field_586e18d3991c2'),(5978,2068,'session_paralela2_2_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5979,2068,'_session_paralela2_2_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d39930b'),(5980,2068,'session_paralela2_2_session_info','Discover the benefits of a combined managed file transfer and workload automation solution. Control-M Managed File Transfer file oriented monitoring and searching capabilities effectively deliver an “inside-out” view of file movement operations in addition to Control-M’s standard job-based views. BMC Control-M Managed File Transfer provides instant visibility into the status of your file transfers and connected endpoints, while leveraging the power and simplicity of a drag-and-drop workflow design interface.  Learn how to minimize the time required to resolve problems and to reduce administration costs.  This session will include and overview of the available features in Control-M MFT, followed by a live demonstration.  Don’t miss the to get all the information that you need to get started!'),(5981,2068,'_session_paralela2_2_session_info','field_586e18d399453'),(5982,2068,'session_paralela2_3_title','Control-M for SAP – Now Stronger than Ever'),(5983,2068,'_session_paralela2_3_title','field_586e18d399076'),(5984,2068,'session_paralela2_3_time','3:00 – 3:45'),(5985,2068,'_session_paralela2_3_time','field_586e18d3991c2'),(5986,2068,'session_paralela2_3_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5987,2068,'_session_paralela2_3_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d39930b'),(5988,2068,'session_paralela2_3_session_info','Control-M support for SAP is stronger than ever. Way back in 2003 Control-M began offering integrations with enterprise applications and the Control-M Option for SAP was the first to be released.  Today, through the Control Module technology, Control-M provides support for managing workloads of dozens of critical business applications. Hear details on the current capabilities of the Control-M for SAP solution and how Control-M can support your SAP environments better than ever before.'),(5989,2068,'_session_paralela2_3_session_info','field_586e18d399453'),(5990,2068,'session_paralela2_4_title','BMC Control-M Roadmap'),(5991,2068,'_session_paralela2_4_title','field_586e18d399076'),(5992,2068,'session_paralela2_4_time','4:00 – 4:45'),(5993,2068,'_session_paralela2_4_time','field_586e18d3991c2'),(5994,2068,'session_paralela2_4_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(5995,2068,'_session_paralela2_4_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d39930b'),(5996,2068,'session_paralela2_4_session_info','Control-M “Next” and other forward-looking topics. Learn how Control-M has powered innovation through automation at one of the largest human capital companies in the world for the last 15 years.'),(5997,2068,'_session_paralela2_4_session_info','field_586e18d399453'),(5998,2068,'session_paralela3_1_title','Best Practices in Capacity Planning and Optimization'),(5999,2068,'_session_paralela3_1_title','field_586e18d3b3b27'),(6000,2068,'session_paralela3_1_time','2:00 – 2:20'),(6001,2068,'_session_paralela3_1_time','field_586e18d3b3c8c'),(6002,2068,'session_paralela3_1_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6003,2068,'_session_paralela3_1_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3b3df1'),(6004,2068,'session_paralela3_1_session_info',''),(6005,2068,'_session_paralela3_1_session_info','field_586e18d3b3f4b'),(6006,2068,'session_paralela3_2_title','Customer Case Study, Actionable Intelligence using filter based reporting'),(6007,2068,'_session_paralela3_2_title','field_586e18d3b3b27'),(6008,2068,'session_paralela3_2_time','2:20 – 2:45'),(6009,2068,'_session_paralela3_2_time','field_586e18d3b3c8c'),(6010,2068,'session_paralela3_2_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6011,2068,'_session_paralela3_2_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3b3df1'),(6012,2068,'session_paralela3_2_session_info','Ben Davies, Senior IT Metrics and Reporting Analyst at a very large insurance company, who is now a Senior Consultant at Moviri will review how to get Actionable Intelligence using the tools and techniques of filter based reporting in BCO. These techniques are independent of how the workspace is organized. These tools and techniques are valid as soon as the first ETLs are implemented.<br/><br/>\r\nAs a Moviri consultant, Ben Davies applied these tools and techniques, delivered Actionable Intelligence within 10 minutes of starting the reports. This is a powerful tool that is relatively easily deployed but takes some practice to use well.'),(6013,2068,'_session_paralela3_2_session_info','field_586e18d3b3f4b'),(6014,2068,'session_paralela3_3_title','The Next Generation Operational Analytics for Evolving IT'),(6015,2068,'_session_paralela3_3_title','field_586e18d3b3b27'),(6016,2068,'session_paralela3_3_time','3:00 – 3:45'),(6017,2068,'_session_paralela3_3_time','field_586e18d3b3c8c'),(6018,2068,'session_paralela3_3_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6019,2068,'_session_paralela3_3_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3b3df1'),(6020,2068,'session_paralela3_3_session_info','Operational analytics gives IT Operations Management (ITOM) teams the right information at the right time. It allows them to quickly focus efforts, reduce time to solve problems, proactively identify issues and optimize performance to support business needs. But what happens when the data needed to perform these tasks is siloed outside of IT Ops or even a company’s IT infrastructure?<br/><br/>\r\nTrueSight Intelligence is a single, architected platform for Operational Analytics that transforms IT and non-IT data generated by digital businesses into meaningful, actionable insights that fuel fast, business-aligned decisions. TrueSight Intelligence captures and ingests real-time streaming data from performance management systems, siloed IT and non-IT systems as well as external sources and then performs analytics and machine learning to correlate data for IT leaders.'),(6021,2068,'_session_paralela3_3_session_info','field_586e18d3b3f4b'),(6022,2068,'session_paralela3_4_title','Proactive Management of Multi Source Cloud Resources and Applications'),(6023,2068,'_session_paralela3_4_title','field_586e18d3b3b27'),(6024,2068,'session_paralela3_4_time','4:00 – 4:45'),(6025,2068,'_session_paralela3_4_time','field_586e18d3b3c8c'),(6026,2068,'session_paralela3_4_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6027,2068,'_session_paralela3_4_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3b3df1'),(6028,2068,'session_paralela3_4_session_info','Cost and faster delivery are the top 2 reasons for selecting cloud. But unless properly managed, these goals will never be realized. Most organizations over-provision infrastructure resources in an attempt to prevent resource shortfalls and application slowdowns or failures, you can’t afford these inefficiencies in cloud services. Choices of capital vs. operational expense, the cost of unused cloud services, and unmanaged cloud services become part of your run rate. The TrueSight products provide you with the insight, analytics, and intelligence you need to understand the cloud infrastructure services you need so you can make responsibly informed fiscal and service decisions.'),(6029,2068,'_session_paralela3_4_session_info','field_586e18d3b3f4b'),(6030,2068,'session_paralela4_1_title','Secure Delivery  –  Ensuring Compliance and Control for Application Pipelines'),(6031,2068,'_session_paralela4_1_title','field_586e18d3cf72b'),(6032,2068,'session_paralela4_1_time','2:00 – 2:25'),(6033,2068,'_session_paralela4_1_time','field_586e18d3cf876'),(6034,2068,'session_paralela4_1_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6035,2068,'_session_paralela4_1_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3cf9bf'),(6036,2068,'session_paralela4_1_session_info','As development models and practices evolve, integrating security and compliance into the application pipeline process becomes even more challenging. Learn how to embed policy checks into your CI/CD process and discover, log, and remediate violations before they creep into your production environment where they can significantly increase your risk of a security or compliance incident. In this session, we will walk through a real-life example of integrating BMC’s new policy service into a modern software delivery process using Rest APIs, and synchronous policy evaluation to drive automated release gateways.'),(6037,2068,'_session_paralela4_1_session_info','field_586e18d3cfb07'),(6038,2068,'session_paralela4_2_title','Killing Virtualization:  Are You Ready for Docker?'),(6039,2068,'_session_paralela4_2_title','field_586e18d3cf72b'),(6040,2068,'session_paralela4_2_time','2:25 – 2:45'),(6041,2068,'_session_paralela4_2_time','field_586e18d3cf876'),(6042,2068,'session_paralela4_2_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6043,2068,'_session_paralela4_2_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3cf9bf'),(6044,2068,'session_paralela4_2_session_info','Docker® makes it easy to create images and deploy applications into containers that run on your laptop, in a virtual machine, or in the cloud. No wonder developers love it. But when it comes to production, treating Docker containers like just another virtual machine can result in undesirable consequences.<br/><br/>\r\nAttend this session to learn how Docker is creating new challenges for operations, and how you can prepare your organization and environment accordingly. We will demonstrate how BMC solutions can be used to deploy, manage, secure, and monitor Docker applications to help you facilitate innovation while maintaining performance, control, and security of your hybrid environment.'),(6045,2068,'_session_paralela4_2_session_info','field_586e18d3cfb07'),(6046,2068,'session_paralela4_3_title','Reduce the Attack Surface And Protect Your Organization with BMC BladeLogic'),(6047,2068,'_session_paralela4_3_title','field_586e18d3cf72b'),(6048,2068,'session_paralela4_3_time','3:00 – 3:25'),(6049,2068,'_session_paralela4_3_time','field_586e18d3cf876'),(6050,2068,'session_paralela4_3_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6051,2068,'_session_paralela4_3_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3cf9bf'),(6052,2068,'session_paralela4_3_session_info','Organizations are discovering that the tools, processes, and teams tasked with protecting the organization aren’t able to cope with the rising tide attacks. While there is media hype around the complex hacking rings trying to topple governments, the scarier news is that most of the time hackers take the far easier path of exploiting known vulnerabilities that have not yet been patched. A strong SecOps solution transforms disconnected initiatives into a comprehensive process that accelerates vulnerability resolution, scales with the business, and mitigates the most damaging risks first. Find out how BMC SecOps solutions let CIOs and CISOs breathe more easily, as they eliminate risks, identify blindspots, and provide the holistic visibility needed for leaders to have confidence in their security posture.'),(6053,2068,'_session_paralela4_3_session_info','field_586e18d3cfb07'),(6054,2068,'session_paralela4_4_title','How Strong is Your Breach Avoidance Strategy?  Live “Hack and Defend” Demo Featuring a White Hat Hacker and BMC Bladelogic Threat Director'),(6055,2068,'_session_paralela4_4_title','field_586e18d3cf72b'),(6056,2068,'session_paralela4_4_time','3:25 – 4:45'),(6057,2068,'_session_paralela4_4_time','field_586e18d3cf876'),(6058,2068,'session_paralela4_4_font_awesome_icon','fa-check'),(6059,2068,'_session_paralela4_4_font_awesome_icon','field_586e18d3cf9bf'),(6060,2068,'session_paralela4_4_session_info','It’s true in sports and it’s true in IT – a strong focus on fundamental skills will lead you to victory. Hackers look for weakness and a disorganized approach to patch management when identifying their targets. If and when you get breached, it will likely involve known vulnerabilities with available fixes. No more excuses, it\'s time to focus on the fundamentals, or get attacked by a novice. Are you ready to block the next attack? Take advantage of this unique opportunity as experts from BMC and experts lead an open dialogue while they demonstrate vulnerability remediation tactics as well as opportunities to speed up reaction times.'),(6061,2068,'_session_paralela4_4_session_info','field_586e18d3cfb07'),(6070,2588,'_wp_attached_file','2017/01/sponsor_logo-xmatters_160x160.jpg'),(6071,2588,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:160;s:6:\"height\";i:160;s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"2017/01/sponsor_logo-xmatters_160x160.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"sponsor_logo-xmatters_160x160-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(6072,2588,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','sponsor logo xmatters'),(6073,2589,'_wp_attached_file','2017/01/sponsor_logo-Turbonomic_160x160.jpg'),(6074,2589,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:160;s:6:\"height\";i:160;s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"2017/01/sponsor_logo-Turbonomic_160x160.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"sponsor_logo-Turbonomic_160x160-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(6075,2590,'_menu_item_type','custom'),(6076,2590,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(6077,2590,'_menu_item_object_id','2590'),(6078,2590,'_menu_item_object','custom'),(6079,2590,'_menu_item_t